English:
../BIOCOM 
shortwave transmission intercepted@29mhz 
meta3.date_stamp(571209.062912) 
 
//transcript follows... 
 
VOICE 1 
State... State of Truth. I don't care... I don't care anymore. I know they'll never find me, but they don't need to. Listeners... is there anyone left? All is silent. Mrs. Truth... gone. I lost... I lost Rocker. My other dog, Billy, died a few weeks ago, and now Rocker. He got... I don't know... I think he had NAM-V. Dogs can get it... I don't know. Excuse me-- Ugh... yeah. Yeah, I guess you know now. I got it. Like everyone else. God knows how. Maybe from Billy. There are no people I could have... I mean, there's nobody left. I'm... I'm going to die. I know that. I have... ah... I have a system set up. A thing... what do you call that... a dead man's switch. When I go, this whole place will burn. I got to do my part. No one else, if there is anyone else, is going to catch it from me, and when my mind goes I don't want to be a Stooper. I can't... I can't think properly so... If you're listening, and you're still healthy, stay away from the animals. It's not just humans, it feeds on life, man. You can't defeat it. Just... hide. That's all I can tell you. Hide. Don't come out, for anything. I think... maybe tonight, it'll be over. Yeah. Tonight. This is my last broadcast. I'm sorry I can't... I wish I had more time with you, but all things must end. I did good work. I'll die with my hand on my heart. Seek the truth America. This is Mr. Truth signing off. 
 
../BIOCOM. 
.. transcript ends// 
intercept log updated 
alert system flagged

状态……真相状态。我不在乎……我不在乎了。我知道他们永远找不到我，但他们不需要。听众们……还有人吗？一切都寂静无声。真理夫人……走了。我输了……我输了洛克。我的另一只狗比利几周前去世了，现在是洛克。他得到了……我不知道……我认为他得到了NAM-V。狗可以得到它...我不知道。对不起——呃……是的。是的，我想你现在知道了。我得到了它。像其他人一样。天知道怎么办。也许来自比利。我已经没有人可以拥有了……我的意思是，已经没有人了。我……我要死了。我知道。我有……啊……我已经建立了一个系统。一个东西……你管它叫什么……死人开关。当我走的时候，整个地方都会被烧毁。我必须尽自己的一份力量。没有其他人，如果有其他人的话，能从我这里得到它，当我的思绪消失时，我不想成为一个弯腰者。我不能……我不能正确思考，所以……如果你在听，而且你仍然健康，请远离动物。它不只是人类，它还以生命为食，伙计。你无法击败它。只是……躲起来。我只能告诉你这些。隐藏。无论如何都别出来。我想……也许今晚，一切就结束了。是的。今晚。这是我最后一次广播。很抱歉我不能...我希望能有更多的时间和你在一起，但一切都必须结束。我做得很好。我会把手放在心上死去。寻求美国的真相。这是真理先生的结束语。

../BIOCOM。
